<p>Modifies the query criteria by changing its <a href="/doc/api/1.1/CDbCriteria#order">CDbCriteria::order</a> property.
This method will use <a href="/doc/api/1.1/CSort#directions">directions</a> to determine which columns need to be sorted.
They will be put in the ORDER BY clause. If the criteria already has non-empty <a href="/doc/api/1.1/CDbCriteria#order">CDbCriteria::order</a> value,
the new value will be appended to it.</p>


